title: Pete Tong Essential Selection 30/01/2009
description:
Pete Tong Essential Selection Friday 30th January 2009

Pete's back and armed with some super hot tunes. 
Paul Van Dyk on the phone for a catch up, as well as Eric Prydz telling us what he has in store for 2009.  
And Soulwax fill us in with their weekend plans on Radio One.

Broadcast: BBC Radio 1, SAT.
